description:
There isn’t a bell loud enough to save this week’s Unqualified guest from Sim’s lifelong love and adoration…the talented Mark-Paul Gosselaar joins Anna and a starstruck Sim today to chat about…

…Saved by the Bell nostalgia

…Prostatitis & cleaning out the “pipes”

…Going from teen heartthrob to well-respected actor

…MP’s Dating Deal Breakers

…a little improv with ‘Kayla’

Catch Mark-Paul Gosselaar on The Passage, every Monday at 9/8c on FOX!

And don’t forget to tune in Thursday to hear Mark-Paul, Anna, and Sim chat with callers!!

 

Follow us!
